# v2 - Conditionals & Loops

## Project 1: Shoot the Enemy

Game text-based, defence attack, shot the enemies untill their strengh 0. Use `while` + `if` on C.

### Learning Concept

- `while` loop intent to looping game di C
- `if` condition intent to validasi input di C
- `scanf` inted to input numeral at C

### Cara Compile & Run

1. `gcc shoot_enemy.c -o shoot`
2. `./shoot`
3. Pencet `1` + press Enter to shoot

